\c 22
\s Mirairo pamusoro pezvevamwe
\p
\v 1 Kana munhu akaba nzombe kana gwai, ndokuriuraya kana kuritengesa, acharipa nzombe shanu panzombe, nemakwai mana pagwai\x + 2 Zvak. 12.6. Zvir. 6.31. Ruk. 19.8.\x*.
\p
\v 2 Kana mbavha ikawanikwa ichipaza, ndokurohwa kusvika yafa\x + Mat. 24.43.\x*, hapana mhosva yeropa kwaari\x + Num.. 35.27.\x*.
\v 3 Kana zuva ramubudira, achava nemhosva yeropa. Anofanira kuripa; kana asina chinhu achatengeswa nekuda kwekuba kwake\x + 21.2.\x*.
\v 4 Kana chakabiwa chikawanikwa zvekuwanikwa muruoko rwake chiri chipenyu\x + 21.16.\x*, ingava nzombe, kana mbongoro, kana gwai, acharipa kaviri\x + 22.1,7.\x*.
\p
\v 5 Kana munhu akadyisa munda kana munda wemizambiringa, akapinza zvipfuwo zvake ndokunodya mumunda weumwe, acharipa pazvakanakisisa zvemunda wake, nepazvakanakisisa zvemunda wake wemizambiringa.
\p
\v 6 Kana moto ukadauka ukabata minzwa kusvika kwapiswa murwi wezviyo kana zviyo zvimire kana munda, wakatungidza moto acharipa zvekuripa.
\p
\v 7 Kana munhu achipa wekwake mari kana nhumbi kuti achengete, zvino zvikabiwa kubva mumba memunhu uyu, kana mbavha ikawanikwa ngaaripe kakapetwa kaviri\x + 22.4.\x*.
\v 8 Kana mbavha ikasawanikwa, ipapo muridzi weimba achaswededzwa kuvatongi\x + 21.6; 22.9.\x*, \add zvionekwe \add*kana asina kuisa ruoko rwake panhumbi dzewekwake.
\v 9 Pashoko rimwe nerimwe rekudarika, panzombe, pambongoro, pagwai, pachekupfeka, pachinhu chipi nechipi chakarasika, munhu achireva kuti ndechake, shoko ravo vari vaviri richaenda kuvatongi\x + 22.8.\x*; vatongi vachapa mhosva acharipa kakapetwa kaviri kune wekwake.
\p
\v 10 Kana munhu achipa wekwake mbongoro kana nzombe kana gwai kana chimwe chipfuwo kuti achengete, \add icho\add* ndokufa kana kukuvara kana kutinhwa pasina anoona;
\v 11 mhiko yaJehovha ichava pakati pavo vari vaviri\x + VaHeb. 6.16.\x*, \add zvionekwe\add* kana asina kuisa ruoko rwake panhumbi dzewekwake; zvino muridzi wazvo achagamuchira; haangaripi.
\v 12 Asi kana zvikabiwa zvirokwazvo kwaari\x + Gen.. 31.39.\x*, acharipa kumuridzi wazvo.
\v 13 Kana zvikabvamburwa-bvamburwa, ngaauye nazvo zvive uchapupu; haangaripi zvakabvamburwa.
\p
\v 14 Zvino kana munhu akakwereta kune wekwake, icho ndokukuvara, kana kufa, muridzi wacho asisipo, ucharipa zvekuripa.
\v 15 Kana muridzi wacho anacho, haangaripi; kana chiri chinhu chakahaiwa,* chavinga kuhaiwa kwacho.
\p
\v 16 Zvino kana munhu akanyengedzera musikana asina kutsidzira kuroorwa\x + Det. 22.28,29.\x*, ndokurara naye, zvirokwazvo achamuroora ave mukadzi wake.
\v 17 Kana baba vake vakaramba zvekuramba kumupa iye, acharipa mari yakaenzana neroora yemhandara\x + Gen.. 34.12. 1 Zvak. 18.25.\x*.
\p
\v 18 Usarega muroyikadzi kuti ararame\x + Det. 18.10,11. Rev. 19.26,31; 20.27. 1 Zvak. 28.3,9.\x*.
\p
\v 19 Ani nani anorara nechipfuwo achaurawa zvirokwazvo\x + Rev. 18.23; 20.15.\x*.
\p
\v 20 Anobaira vamwari kunze kwaJehovha chete achaparadzwa chose\x + Num.. 25.2,7,8. Det. 13.1,2,5,6,9,13,14,15; 17.2,3,5.\x*.
\p
\v 21 Usadzvinyirira mutorwa kana kumumanikidza, nokuti maiva vatorwa munyika yeEgipita\x + 23.9. Rev. 19.33. Rev. 25.35. Det. 10.18,19. Jer. 7.6. Zek. 7.10. Mara. 3.5.\x*.
\p
\v 22 Usatambudza chero chirikadzi kana nherera\x + Det. 10.18; 24.17; 27.19. Map. 94.6. Isa. 1.17,23; 10.2. Eze. 22.7. Zek. 7.10. Jak. 1.27.\x*.
\v 23 Kana ukavatambudza zvekuvatambudza, zvirokwazvo kana vakadana kwazvo kwandiri\x + Job. 34.28; 35.9. Det. 15.9; 24.15. Ruk. 18.7.\x*, zvirokwazvo ndichanzwa kudana kwavo\x + 22.27. Map. 18.6; 145.19. Jak. 5.4.\x*;
\v 24 zvino hasha dzangu dzichapfuta\x + Map. 69.24.\x* ndigokuurayai nemunondo, zvino vakadzi venyu vachava chirikadzi nevana venyu nherera\x + Map. 109.9. Marir. 5.3.\x*.
\p
\v 25 Kana uchikweretesa mari kuvanhu vangu varombo vanewe\x + Rev. 25.35,36,37. Det. 23.19,20. Neh. 5.7. Map. 15.5. Zvir. 28.8. Eze. 18.8,13,17; 22.12.\x*, usazviita semukweretesi; usaisa pamusoro pake zvibereko.
\v 26 Kana ukatongotora nguvo yewekwako ruve rubatso\x + Det. 24.6,10,13,17. Job. 22.6; 24.3,9. Zvir. 20.16. Eze. 18.7,16. Amo. 2.8. Zvir. 22.27.\x*, uidzosere kwaari zuva risati ravira;
\v 27 nokuti ndicho chifukidzo chake chega, inguvo yake yeganda rake; acharara pai? Zvino zvichaitika kana akadana kwandiri, ndichanzwa, nokuti\x + 22.23.\x* ndine tsitsi\x + 34.6. 2 Makor. 30.9. Neh. 9.17. Map. 86.15; 103.8.\x*.
\p
\v 28 Usarerusa Mwari, uye\x + 21.17. 2 Zvak. 19.21. Mup. 10.20. Jud. 8. Mab. 23.5.\x* usatuka mubati pakati pevanhu vako.
\p
\v 29 Usanonosa chibereko chakazara nemuto wenyu wezvibereko; dangwe revanakomana venyu uchapa kwandiri.
\p\x + 13.2; 13.12; 34.19.\x*
\v 30 Uite saizvozvo nenzombe dzako \add ne\add*makwai\x + Det. 15.19.\x* ako; richava namai varo mazuva manomwe\x + Rev. 22.27.\x*; nezuva rerusere ucharipa kwandiri.
\p
\v 31 Zvino muchava vanhu vatsvene kwandiri; naizvozvo\x + 19.6.\x* musadya nyama yakabvamburwa nezvikara musango; muchaikandira kuimbwa\x + Rev. 22.8. Eze. 4.14; 44.31.\x*.